    "**[EN]** Overview of the tasks provided by Elastic MCP Server for interaction with Elasticsearch data.<br>\n",
    "**[KR]** Elastic MCP 서버가 제공하는 Elasticsearch 데이터와 상호작용할 수 있는 Task 개요."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Elastic MCP Server Tasks Overview\n",
    "\n",
    "Once the MCP Server and Claude Desktop are configured, you can use the following tasks provided by Elastic's MCP Server through natural language queries in Claude Desktop:\n",
    "\n",
    "- `list_indices`: List all available indices in the Elasticsearch cluster.\n",
    "- `get_mappings`: Retrieve field mappings for a specific index.\n",
    "- `search`: Perform a search using Elasticsearch Query DSL (focus of this demo).\n",
    "- `get_shards`: Get shard information for indices."
   ]
  }
